data.description: Charming 3 bed, 1.5 bath ranch home with beautiful country view.  This home has many recent updates:  painting, flooring in kitchen and baths and light fixtures.  The main bathroom has a new vanity and toilet.  The kitchen has new paint and backsplash.  This home also includes hardwood floors, a Fisher woodstove, arched doorways, French doors, insulated windows and new paint in most rooms.  There is an attached 2 car garage with garage door openers.  Both the front and back porches have porch swings to enjoy the view.  You can see the New River Bridge and Shot Tower.  The front porch is 200 sq feet and the back porch is 344 sq feet and a low maintenance vinyl fence surrounds the entire yard.  The home has a split floor plan with the main bedroom and half bath off the living room and the other 2 bedrooms and main bath are just past the kitchen and dining area.
